{"tid":1557460,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【BNO IS PART OF COMMONWEALTH 】130名英國國會議員助陣 BNO","createTime":"2019-09-10T06:23:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T10:16:57.000Z","uid":139698,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cf618a7b8cbda5bb40e6eddea49245051937742a","tid":1557460,"uid":139698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T06:23:03.000Z","msg":"前港督彭定康及接近130名英國國會議員，向英國外相藍韜文(Dominic Raab)發聯署信，呼籲英聯邦國家給予香港居民第二公民身份及居留權。<br />\n<br />\n聯署信要求將有關討論，列入明年在盧旺達舉行的英聯邦政府領導人會議議程。<br />\n<br />\n現時，眾多香港居民持有稱為BNO的英國國民(海外)護照，但不享有英國居留權。藍韜文早前表明，如果更改規定，可能會破壞「一國兩制」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咪撚再消費 「一國兩制」，名存實亡左好撚耐喇<br />\n<br />\n支持澳洲政府給予保護簽證居澳港人<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/prime-minister-mr-scott-morrison-protect-the-pro-democracy-hongkongers-in-australia?utm_content=bandit-starter_cl_share_content_en-au:v12&amp;recruited_by_id=f7fe5230-8c97-11e8-a0c0-bfb104ace612&amp;recruiter=889993192&amp;utm_source=share_petition&amp;utm_medium=copylink&amp;utm_campaign=share_petition\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fprime-minister-mr-scott-morrison-protect-the-pro-democracy-hongkongers-in-australia%3Futm_content%3Dbandit-starter_cl_share_content_en-au%3Av12%26recruited_by_id%3Df7fe5230-8c97-11e8-a0c0-bfb104ace612%26recruiter%3D889993192%26utm_source%3Dshare_petition%26utm_medium%3Dcopylink%26utm_campaign%3Dshare_petition&d=SMAvs7Hy8J1z03%2F%2B44sdD%2FTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=95f991b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/prime-minister-mr-scott-morrison-protect-the-pro-democracy-hongkongers-in-australia?utm_content=bandit-starter_cl_share_content_en-au:v12&amp;recruited_by_id=f7fe5230-8c97-11e8-a0c0-bfb104ace612&amp;recruiter=889993192&amp;utm_source=share_petition&amp;utm_medium=copylink&amp;utm_campaign=share_petition</a>"},{"pid":"b11edfd37363438884152b3ee0c8251e5809d749","tid":1557460,"uid":13349,"like":0,"disli